# Git Commit Preferences

- **Sole author**: All commits must be authored only by Aditya (`adityaguptavns1@gmail.com`).
- **No co-authors**: Never add `Co-authored-by`, `Signed-off-by`, or any trailer attributing other contributors.
- **Sole contribution**: Commits should reflect only Aditya's work — no mixed attribution or bot co-author lines.
- **Do not change git config** to set identity; use the existing configured author.
- **Commit style**: Use concise `feat:` / `fix:` / `chore:` prefixes matching existing history.
- **Push**: Only push when explicitly requested.
